WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.593
I only ever wished to offer you comfort.

00:01.617 --> 00:03.217
Comfort was not worth tasting.

00:03.297 --> 00:06.789
Temperance Yeardley told me
I must remarry. And quickly.

00:06.851 --> 00:09.285
Every instinct makes me fight
against such a confinement.

00:09.340 --> 00:11.620
I am sick

00:11.700 --> 00:14.447
of the likes of you vermin!

00:14.486 --> 00:16.660
You said I was...

00:16.740 --> 00:19.620
I've heard tell of men,
Master Massinger,

00:19.700 --> 00:20.700
made blind with rage.

00:20.780 --> 00:24.140
Tell the governor that you found
the secretary on his knees.

00:24.220 --> 00:26.820
It will make no difference.
He already possesses me.

00:26.900 --> 00:30.860
And that is why he refuses
to suspect you as the Spanish spy.

00:30.948 --> 00:33.374
No, he already knows who that is.

00:33.429 --> 00:35.589
Does it say if Governor Yeardley's
cargo was also lost?

00:35.620 --> 00:37.060
No, it doesn't say that.

00:37.140 --> 00:39.660
Ours is stolen, but his is safe.
In't that suspicious?

00:39.740 --> 00:42.860
If Yeardley believes he's seen
the last of the Sharrows' anger,

00:42.940 --> 00:44.220
then he will need new eyes.

